        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Acts 15:5",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") thus put forward here afresh, was not confined to themselves (Schwanbeck, who here assumes a confusion of sources), but took place in presence, and with the assistance, of the whole church assembled together, as is evident from ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Acts 15:12",
        "children": []
